name: Katun Corporation
overview: Katun Corporation supplies imaging supplies, photoreceptors, and parts for the office equipment industry. It offers laser and fax parts, laser and fax toner cartridges, ink jet cartridges, printers, imaging supplies, and copier parts. The company also offers service accessories, including vacuums, cleaners, supplies and lubricants, tools, and copy control systems. It offers its products through hard-copy catalogues and online. The company was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Minneapolis, Minnesota. It has business units in North America, Europe, Africa, the Middle East, Latin America, Asia, and Pacific. Katun Corporation is a former subsidiary of PNA Holdings, L.L.C.

milestones.description: Katun Corporation Acquires the Toner Cartridge Business of Media Sciences International, Inc.
